SurgicalCaseFact

The surgical case fact contains information about surgical and invasive procedural cases. Each row represents a case.

For Epic data, the fact includes information from cases (ORC) and logs (ORL).

Properties

Reporting table name
dbo.SurgicalCaseFact
Granularity
A surgical case
